Kern Las Vegas Cc Patti Stacey The new Las Vegas Pool product will bridge into sitara as Pipe Kern River Gas Transmission Zone Las Vegas Facility UNA Las Vegas It is buyers choice the pool consists of Harry Allen Apex Blue Diamond Pecos Lone Mountain Pecos and Lone Mountain do not seem to be options when manually booking a deal in sitara If they are not in the system they probably need to be set up The meters will be determined before during scheduling The deals will bridge with the UNA Las Vegas meterfacility Let me know what you think Thanks Jason
